articles.title: IEX total volume jumps 56% YoY to 13,250 MU in July - CNBCTV18
articles.description: IEX achieved electricity volume of 10,093 MU in July'24, marking a 29% year on year increase. Green electricity volume for the month stood at 1 billion unit, a 259% growth YoY.
